OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776784267
OL,3,CTube strike set to hit hospitality as
OL,4,Cunion warns of 'a lot of bad feeling'
OL,6,FPubs and restaurants in London fear
OL,7,Fthat this week's strikes by London
OL,8,FUnderground drivers will have a big
OL,9,Fimpact on their business.
OL,11,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,12,FTransport union will walk out from 12
OL,13,Fnoon for 24 hours today and again on
OL,14,FThursday, disrupting services for the
OL,15,Frest of the week.
OL,17,FTransport for London urged passengers
OL,18,Fto check before they travel, warning
OL,19,Fthat the industrial action will hit
OL,20,Fservices.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
