PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776784267
OL,3,CTube strike set to hit hospitality as
OL,4,Cunion warns of 'a lot of bad feeling'
OL,6,FRMT members were mounting picket lines
OL,7,Foutside Tube stations from the start
OL,8,Fof the strike.
OL,10,FRMT official Jared Wood said union
OL,11,Fmembers felt strongly about the issues
OL,12,Fat the heart of the dispute.
OL,14,FHe said the row was not just about a
OL,15,Ffour-day week, saying other issues
OL,16,Fwere involved such as the length of
OL,17,Fshifts and changes to annual leave.
OL,19,FHe said: "TfL need to come forward
OL,20,Fwith changes to their proposals for
OL,21,Fthis dispute to be resolved.
OL,26,@{D@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776784267
OL,3,CTube strike set to hit hospitality as
OL,4,Cunion warns of 'a lot of bad feeling'
OL,6,F"There is absolute unanimity among our
OL,7,Fmembers that we have to fight these
OL,8,Fproposals."Mr Wood said there was now
OL,9,F"a lot of bad feeling" between the
OL,10,Fdrivers and London Underground.
OL,12,FEmma McClarkin, chief executive of the
OL,13,FBritish Beer and Pub Association,
OL,14,Fsaid: "In a typical week, London's
OL,15,Fpubs generate approximately #80
OL,16,Fmillion in gross added value between
OL,17,FTuesday and Friday alone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@KO]qD@AOUqD@VO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
