OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776784267
OL,3,CTube strike set to hit hospitality as
OL,4,Cunion warns of 'a lot of bad feeling'
OL,6,F"This doesn't just boost the economy
OL,7,Fbut represents the jobs, high streets,
OL,8,Fand community spirit that revolve
OL,9,Faround pubs.
OL,11,F"At a time when so many locals are
OL,12,Falready operating on a knife edge
OL,13,Fbecause of huge costs, significant
OL,14,Fdisruption to trade will be acutely
OL,15,Ffelt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
