OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776784267
OL,3,CTube strike set to hit hospitality as
OL,4,Cunion warns of 'a lot of bad feeling'
OL,6,F"It's vital that that overall cost of
OL,7,Fdoing business comes down, which is
OL,8,Fwhy we're working with Government on
OL,9,Fways to support the pub, including
OL,10,Fpermanent business rates reform, a cut
OL,11,Fin beer duty and VAT, and a reduction
OL,12,Fof the regulatory burden."
OL,14,FSome bus routes in the capital
OL,15,Foperated by Stagecoach will be
OL,16,Faffected by a separate 24-hour strike
OL,17,Ffrom 5am on Friday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
