OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776784267
OL,3,CTube strike set to hit hospitality as
OL,4,Cunion warns of 'a lot of bad feeling'
OL,6,FClaire Mann, TfL's chief operating
OL,7,Fofficer, said: "We have set out
OL,8,Fproposals to the RMT for a four-day
OL,9,Fworking week.
OL,11,F"This allows us to offer train
OL,12,Foperators an additional day off,
OL,13,Fwhilst at the same time bringing
OL,14,FLondon Underground in line with the
OL,15,Fworking patterns of other train
OL,16,Foperating companies, improving
OL,17,Freliability and flexibility at no
OL,18,Fadditional cost.
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
